'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/162738/', '', 'Cholecalciferol, Vosoritide', 'Cinacalcet, Doxercalciferol, Salmon calcitonin, Calcifediol, Paricalcitol', 1767369485);
